  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nExecutingDirectory set in [PathUtils](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/master/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Logging/PathUtils.cs#L38) not correctly. Currently it uses directory name of executed binary, which is wrong.\r\nSo, when Nethermind executed from /somewhere/nethermind directory by running /usr/bin/Nethermind.Runner it will crash. Because process could not create log directory in /usr/bin/\r\n\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. copy Nethermind binary to /usr/bin/nethermind\r\n2. cd /data/nethermind\r\n3. /usr/bin/nethermind --datadir /data/nethermind --config mainnet \r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nClient is running\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\n```\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]: 2021-08-30 16-06-37.4713|Setting LogDirectory to: /data/nethermind/logs, from: logs\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]: Unhandled exception. System.UnauthorizedAccessException: Access to the path '/usr/bin/logs' is denied.\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:  ---> System.IO.IOException: Permission denied\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    --- End of inner exception stack trace ---\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    at System.IO.FileSystem.CreateDirectory(String fullPath)\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    at System.IO.Directory.CreateDirectory(String path)\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    at Nethermind.Logging.NLog.NLogLogger.Init(String fileName, String logDirectory)\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    at Nethermind.Logging.NLog.NLogLogger..ctor(String fileName, String logDirectory, String loggerName)\r\nAug 30 16:06:37 host-2 nethermind[20009]:    at Nethermind.Runner.Program.Main(String[] args)\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Debian\r\n - Version 1.11.0\r\n\r\n\r\n",
